parameters.name: Accessibility
parameters.description:
The visibility of the jobs. Valid values:

*   PUBLIC: The jobs are public in the workspace.
*   PRIVATE: The jobs are visible only to you and the administrator of the workspace.

parameters.name: MaxRunningTimeMinutes
parameters.description: The maximum running time. Unit: minutes.

parameters.name: TensorboardId
parameters.description: The ID of the TensorBoard instance. For more information about how to query the ID of the TensorBoard instance, see [ListTensorboards](~~459689~~).
